ed him into the top tier of California&#39;s governor race</title><updateDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 09:00:40 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Natasha Korecki</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 19:59:44 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Illinois Gov. JB Pritzker may be a billionaire, but should the Democrat run for president in 2028, he may for the first time accept fundraising dollars, NBC News has learned</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2028-election/billionaire-illinois-gov-jb-pritzker-not-fully-self-finance-2028-run-rcna343122</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2028-election/billionaire-illinois-gov-jb-pritzker-not-fully-self-finance-2028-run-rcna343122</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-Pritzker-vsb-1702-6609fa.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Angelina Katsanis</media:credit><media:text type="plain">J.B. Pritzker</media:text><media:description type="plain">Illinois Gov. J.B. Pritzker speaks at the National Action Network Convention in New York, on April 9.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-04/260430-Pritzker-vsb-1702-6609fa.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 19:59:44 GMT</pubDate><title>Billionaire Gov. JB Pritzker explores something new in 2028: Raising money</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 21:36:59 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Henry J. Gomez</dc:creator><dateTimeWritten>Sat, 02 May 2026 00:00:34 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>President Donald Trump moved Friday to thin the Republican field running for Senate in Kentucky, endorsing Rep.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/2026-election/trump-endorses-rep-andy-barr-kentucky-senate-primary-r